author: RTÉ News
title: Teen claiming to have virus allegedly spat at garda
description: A young man has been charged in relation to an incident in Cork where he allegedly spat at a garda while claiming to have the coronavirus.
content:
A young man has been charged in relation to an incident in Cork where he allegedly spat at a garda while claiming to have the coronavirus.
